WEBVTT

1
00:51:39.580 --> 00:51:42.380 
她先发制人  解雇了四名内阁成员
She preemptively fired four members of her Cabinet.

2
00:51:43.140 --> 00:51:45.270 
沃纳请求最高法院
Warner's petitioning the Supreme Court

3
00:51:45.870 --> 00:51:48.180 
裁定她行为的合法性
to rule on the legality of her action.

4
00:51:49.030 --> 00:51:51.900 
-那你有什么计划  -依我的要求
- So what's your plan? - At my request,

5
00:51:52.380 --> 00:51:54.610 
总统要求在俄国安委
the President's demanded immediate and high-level talks

6
00:51:54.610 --> 00:51:56.470 
即刻进行
with my counterparts

7
00:51:56.470 --> 00:51:58.800 
高级别对话
on the Russian national security council.

8
00:51:59.070 --> 00:52:01.420 
作为抓捕西蒙妮行动的掩护吗
As the pretext for an operation to grab Simone?

9
00:52:01.420 --> 00:52:03.020 
代表团今晚就出发
Delegation leaves tonight.

10
00:52:07.210 --> 00:52:08.390 
现在会不会太迟了
Is it too late?

11
00:52:09.000 --> 00:52:10.060 
什么太迟
For?

12
00:52:10.580 --> 00:52:12.760 
加我进去  我想我应该能帮上忙
Me to join? I think I could be useful.

